name: Fortnite: Dark Reflections Pack
summary:
Did the Cube ever corrupt, or was the darkness always there? Let your dark side take control while wearing the Dark Reflections pack. Includes the following cosmetics:

- Dark Wild Card Outfit
- Wild Cube Back Bling
- Dark Red Knight Outfit
- Dark Shield Back Bling
- Dark Jonesy Outfit
- Dark Axe Pickaxe
